39 occupied vehicles in the roadway.
40 (2) "Course of conduct" does not include constitutionally protected
41 activity or conduct that is necessary to accomplish a lawful purpose.
42 (d) A person who violates the provisions of this section may also be
43 prosecuted for, convicted of and punished for any offense in chapter 21 of

